----------------------------------------------------------
  INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS
----------------------------------------------------------

• Build Granite

  1) Grab the source:
      $ bzr branch lp:granite

  2) Configure:
      $ cd granite
      $ mkdir build
      $ cd build
      $ cmake .. -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr

  3) Build library and demo application:
     $ make

  4) Install (may need root privileges, e.g. using 'sudo')
     # make install

  5) Build API documentation (optional)

     • Vala API:
       $ make valadocs

     • C API:
       $ make cdocs

     • Both targets:
       $ make docs

• Bugs

  If you find bugs in this installation guide or in Granite itself,
  please report them at:

      https://launchpad.net/granite/+filebug
